<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1186.95203.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Type specimen of Stelis siamensis Friese, 1904, male, from Nan province, Thailand, which was recently synonymized with Bathanthidium (Manthidium) binghami (Friese, 1901) A lateral view B dorsal view C posterior angle of metasoma D original label E face F dorsal of metasoma. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/954859" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

